/**
 * Step 1: Clean up existing data before the variety @@unique constraint.
 *
 * Problem: @@unique([scientificName]) meant only 1 record per species existed.
 * The variety seeder was overwriting the same record for each variety of a species.
 *
 * Solution: For each scientificName that has a base record (variety=NULL or empty)
 * AND variety-specific records trying to be added — keep BOTH as separate records.
 *
 * This script:
 * - Finds all species that need variety-specific records
 * - Duplicates the base record for each variety, then sets the variety field
 *
 * Run: cd green-thumb && ./node_modules/.bin/tsx scripts/seed-varieties.ts
 */

